FBIS4-20035 "drweu080_h_94009" FBIS-WEU-94-080 Daily Report 26 Apr 1994 GERMANY Major Development Aid Promised to India Major Development Aid Promised to India AU2204181594 Duesseldorf HANDELSBLATT in German 22-23 Apr 94 p 12 AU2204181594 Duesseldorf HANDELSBLATT German BFN ["vwd." report: "Again Major Development Aid for India"] [Text] Bonn -- Within the framework of bilateral development cooperation with India, the Federal Government has now promised the country 315 billion German marks [DM] for financial cooperation and DM36.5 billion for technical cooperation. The FRG Government is increasingly concentrating its development policy cooperation with India on programs to combat poverty and for environmental protection.
